there she finds a renewed discovery of her people and native culture. Larry brings his intimate relationship to Morocco into this: he first got a nose for leather in Fes, before taking up working with it for a quarter of a century; over the past 9 years he has been trading directly with fine craftsmen there. Add a life-long love of travel, teaching and Adult Learning and you have the ideal hosts.\r\n\r\nOur last organised journey was in 2012, the next is likely to be later in 2016. We are always interested in exploring ideas and requests for further Journeys, so if you would like any further information, or to receive news of future Journeys, please contact us with your details.\r\nCall Larry Leighton on 01453 755370 or use <a href=\"/contact\">the contact form</a>.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" transparent_background=\"off\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" padding_mobile=\"off\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" module_id=\"contact\"][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Title: Opening Times\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\n<h1>Opening Times</h1>\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Opening times text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\nThe Golden Fleece Warehouse is open every Friday and Saturday\r\nfrom 11.00 am to 5.30 pm\r\n\r\nFind us at:\r\nUnit 16D &amp; E,\r\nGriffin Mill,\r\nLondon Rd. Thrupp,\r\nStroud, GL5 2AZ\r\n(opposite Bailleys Paints)\r\n\r\n[/e